 &lt;BR&gt; 
2. The Government of India, vide Taxation Laws (Amendment) Act, 2019, inserted section 115BAA in Income Tax Act, 1961 which provides domestic Companies an irrevocable option to pay corporate Income Tax at reduced rate (i.e., 25.17%) subject to non availment of certain incentives and allowances under different provisions of Act.  The Company is in the process of evaluating the availment of said option. &lt;BR&gt; 
 &lt;BR&gt; 
